1 land. No provision in this Article shall apply to any railroad which owns,
2 operates, or permits facilities under land which the railroad owns or operates.
3 (8) An excavation of a grave space, as defined in G.S. 65-48(10), the installation
4 of a monument or memorial at a grave space, or an excavation related to the
5 placement of a temporary structure or tent by a cemetery regulated under
